# AniList API Token for authenticated tests
# You can get this from https://anilist.co/settings/developer
# 1. Create a new API Client
# 2. Copy the Client ID
# 3. Go to https://anilist.co/api/v2/oauth/authorize?client_id=YOUR_CLIENT_ID&response_type=token
# 4. Authorize and copy the access_token from the URL
ANILIST_TOKEN=your_access_token_here
